---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Wix Studio Development Agency"
  description="Create polished Wix Studio websites with fluid design, custom Velo logic, and low-maintenance infrastructure for service brands and fast-moving teams."
  keywords="wix studio development, wix studio agency, velo development, wix website design"
>
  <section class="relative pt-36 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-surface">
    <!-- Backlights -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-primary-maroon/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(193,199,207,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(193,199,207,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
      
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-accent hover:text-white transition-colors uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-8 focus:outline-none">
        ← Back to Overview
      </a>

      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20 bg-blue-500/5 text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-400 tracking-[0.1em] uppercase mb-4">
          Visual Accelerator
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
          Wix Studio Development. <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-silver via-white to-primary-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent">No Maintenance. Just Speed.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-secondary-silver leading-relaxed">
          Stunning interactive animations and premium fluid typography without server maintenance overhead. We build pixel-perfect structures using Wix Studio's engine and extend functionality using custom Velo JavaScript code.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Specs & Performance Highlights -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20">
        <div class="p-6 border border-outline-ghost bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70 font-semibold block mb-2">Time-to-Market</span>
          <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white block mb-1">14 Days Launch</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-secondary-silver">Rapid UI development phase bypassing traditional database configuration.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-outline-ghost bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70 font-semibold block mb-2">Maintenance Cost</span>
          <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white block mb-1">$0.00 Server Fees</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-secondary-silver">Managed infrastructure with automatic security patches and scaling.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-outline-ghost bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70 font-semibold block mb-2">Interactive Depth</span>
          <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white block mb-1">Custom Velo Scripting</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-secondary-silver">Wix database pipelines, dynamic search models, and bookings flows.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-20" id="animations">
        
        <!-- Left Column: Key Capabilities -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Wix Studio Capabilities</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-default bg-primary-maroon/20 border border-primary-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-accent shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">01</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" id="migration">Figma-to-Wix Studio</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/90 leading-relaxed">
                  Translating responsive Figma mockups into fluid layouts. We configure grid nesting, docking ratios, and custom breakpoints for an identical appearance across small mobile viewports and large desktop screens.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-default bg-primary-maroon/20 border border-primary-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-accent shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">02</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" id="velo">Velo API & Database Engineering</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/90 leading-relaxed">
                  Extending the basic builder capabilities. We write custom JavaScript using Velo APIs to manage collections, fetch external data nodes, configure user filters, and handle booking/reservation scripts.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-default bg-primary-maroon/20 border border-primary-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-accent shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">03</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" id="headless">Hybrid Wix Headless</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/90 leading-relaxed">
                  Leveraging Wix's back-end booking engine, commerce catalogs, and user databases while serving the UI from other custom frameworks, maintaining maximum architecture flexibility.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Specifications Detail Card -->
        <div class="p-8 border border-outline-ghost/40 bg-surface-container rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-primary-maroon/10 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs border-b border-outline-ghost/20 pb-4">Wix Studio Specifications</h3>
          
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">Layout Engine</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Flexbox, CSS Grid, Fluid Typography</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">Developer Scripting</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Velo JavaScript (Node.js runtime)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">Database Support</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Wix Data Collections, External DB Sync</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">Headless Coverage</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Wix Headless APIs (Commerce, Bookings)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">Hosting Infrastructure</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Wix Multi-Cloud (AWS + Google Cloud)</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          
          <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-ghost/50 rounded-default text-xs text-on-surface-variant">
            <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Visual Accelerator Program:</strong> We help clients launch beautiful sites in days, hand off a dynamic CMS editor dashboard, and avoid ongoing retainer developers dependencies.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Action Footer -->
      <div class="p-8 border border-primary-accent/20 bg-primary-maroon/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Ready to design a rapid visual experience?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary-silver">Book a tech strategy call to explore a clean, zero-maintenance Wix Studio architecture.</p>
        </div>
        <a 
          href="/#contact" 
          class="w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-primary-maroon border border-primary-accent/40 rounded-default glow-btn-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-lg text-center"
        >
          Book Strategy Call
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 md:py-28 bg-surface border-t border-outline-ghost/30">
    <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 max-w-[760px] mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-primary-accent/20 bg-primary-maroon/10 text-[10px] font-bold text-primary-accent tracking-[0.16em] uppercase mb-5">
          Wix FAQs
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-5">
          Wix Studio Questions Answered
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-secondary-silver leading-relaxed">
          These FAQs cover Wix Studio builds, migration, Velo scripting, and the benefits of a no-maintenance visual platform.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4">
        <details class="group rounded-lg border border-outline-ghost/50 bg-surface-container-low p-6 md:p-7" open>
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">What is Wix Studio used for?</span>
            <span class="text-2xl text-primary-accent transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant/90">
            Wix Studio is often used for visually rich websites, service-based brands, launch campaigns, and teams that need a polished experience without a traditional development-heavy maintenance load.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-lg border border-outline-ghost/50 bg-surface-container-low p-6 md:p-7">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Can you migrate a site into Wix Studio from another platform?</span>
            <span class="text-2xl text-primary-accent transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant/90">
            Yes. We can help restructure content, rebuild layouts, and preserve essential SEO and user journey elements when migrating into Wix Studio.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-lg border border-outline-ghost/50 bg-surface-container-low p-6 md:p-7">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">What is Velo and when is it useful?</span>
            <span class="text-2xl text-primary-accent transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant/90">
            Velo is Wix's scripting layer that allows custom logic, database interactions, bookings flows, and dynamic website behavior beyond standard builder capabilities.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group rounded-lg border border-outline-ghost/50 bg-surface-container-low p-6 md:p-7">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-left">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Is Wix Studio a good option for startups and service companies?</span>
            <span class="text-2xl text-primary-accent transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant/90">
            It is often an excellent fit when speed, visual polish, and simple ongoing maintenance matter more than building a large custom software platform from scratch.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is Wix Studio used for?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Wix Studio is often used for visually rich websites, service-based brands, launch campaigns, and teams that need a polished experience without a traditional development-heavy maintenance load."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can you migrate a site into Wix Studio from another platform?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. We can help restructure content, rebuild layouts, and preserve essential SEO and user journey elements when migrating into Wix Studio."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is Velo and when is it useful?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Velo is Wix's scripting layer that allows custom logic, database interactions, bookings flows, and dynamic website behavior beyond standard builder capabilities."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is Wix Studio a good option for startups and service companies?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "It is often an excellent fit when speed, visual polish, and simple ongoing maintenance matter more than building a large custom software platform from scratch."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
</script>
